data.description: Highest and Best due 6/16 at 12 noon. Wonderfully maintained and clean as a whistle!  This beautiful home has been updated with new plush carpet, laminate hardwoods, ceramic tile and more.  Freshly painted and move in ready. AC size increased to support enclosing the attached garage for additional space if desired.  Spacious, level, and shaded yard. Roof replaced in 2013.  Oversized 2 Car Detached Garage/Workshop with power and attic space.  (Peg boards included). Multi level back deck with private covered lounge/patio area that is perfect for entertaining guests, adding a hot tub, or just relaxing at the end of the day.  Septic tank cleaned 11/2017. Walk in closets in 2 of the bedrooms, Faux wood blinds, Kitchen with pantry. Custom built swing set included!
data.whatILove: What I love best about our home is our quiet neighborhood with great neighbors, a wonderful place to raise children & grandchildren. The backyard is like a private little park with plenty of room to relax & play. It’ is close to schools, church, grocery stores & some great restaurants.
